ate: Language files</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h4>Version 1.2.6 - Released on Oct 03, 2018</h4>\n        <ul>\n        	<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.5.0 RC1</li>\n			<li>Update: Plugin framework</li>\n			<li>Update: Language file</li>\n        </ul>\n         <h4>Version 1.2.5 - Released on May 26, 2018 </h4>\n            <ul>\n                <li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.4.0</li>\n                <li>New: Support to WordPress 4.9.6</li>\n                <li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n                <li>Update: Dutch language</li>\n                <li>Update: Italian language</li>\n            </ul>\n        <h4>Version 1.2.4 - Released on Apr 10, 2018 </h4>\n	        <ul>\n				<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.3.4</li>\n				<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.9.5</li>\n				<li>New: Show tab layout info in Table list</li>\n				<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n				<li>Fix: Tab content not deleted in the product data</li>\n	        </ul>\n  		<h4>Version 1.2.3 - Released on Feb 07, 2018 </h4>\n	        <ul>\n	           	<li>New: Integration with YITH Frontend Manager for WooCommerce version 1.4.0</li>\n				<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.3.1</li>\n				<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.9.4</li>\n				<li>Update: Plugin Framework 3.0.12</li>\n	        </ul>\n        <h4>Version 1.2.2 - Released on Jan 23, 2018 </h4>\n        <ul>\n            <li>New: Dutch language file</li>\n			<li>Fix: Image gallery issue</li>\n			<li>Fix: Form type issue</li>\n			<li>Update: Plugin Framework</li>\n        </ul>\n          <h4>Version 1.2.1 - Released on Dec 12, 2017 </h4>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Fix: WPML issue with tab showing up in every language</li>\n            <li>Fix: Contact form doesn\'t display on frontend</li>\n            <li>Update: Plugin Framework 3.0.1</li>\n        </ul>\n         <h4>Version 1.2.0 - Released on Dec 11, 2017 </h4>\n        <ul>\n        	<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.2.5</li>\n			<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.9.1</li>\n	